## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b3cc2-189">Se il <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> viene `Output`e l'esecuzione dell'oggetto associato <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand> non restituisce un valore, il <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter> conterrà un valore null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3cc2-189">If the <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> is `Output`, and execution of the associated <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand> does not return a value, the <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter> will contain a null value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b3cc2-190">I valori null vengono gestiti usando il <xref:System.DBNull> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3cc2-190">Null values are handled using the <xref:System.DBNull> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b3cc2-191">`Output`, `InputOut`, e `ReturnValue` parametri restituiti chiamando <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> non è possibile accedere fino a quando non si chiama <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader.Close%2A> o `Dispose` sul <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3cc2-191">`Output`, `InputOut`, and `ReturnValue` parameters returned by calling <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> cannot be accessed until you call <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader.Close%2A> or `Dispose` on the <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b3cc2-192">L'esempio seguente crea un <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter> e vengono impostate alcune delle relative proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3cc2-192">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateMyProc(connection As OdbcConnection)  
  
   Dim command As OdbcCommand = connection.CreateCommand()  
   command.CommandText = "{ call MyProc(?,?,?) }"  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Int).Value = 1  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 2  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 3  
  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateMyProc(OdbcConnection connection)   
{  
   OdbcCommand command = connection.CreateCommand();  
   command.CommandText = "{ call MyProc(?,?,?) }";  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Int).Value = 1;  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 2;  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 3;  
}  
```

  
  
